videos.title: Built From Scratch
videos.description: After a summer of preparation and construction, the Broncos play their first game against dominant Danville.

videos.title: Home Field Advantage
videos.description: The Broncos first home game comes with another welcome first.

videos.title: Facing Tradition
videos.description: On a winning streak, the Broncos face central Kentucky powerhouse Scott County.

videos.title: Kings of Lexington
videos.description: As the team wraps up the regular season, a homecoming king is crowned and the team takes the top spot in town.

videos.title: Changing colors
videos.description: For these two Broncos, starting at a new school is old news.

videos.title: Survive and Advance
videos.description: Time for playoffs. The Broncos face two familiar opponents in the first two rounds.

videos.title: Rematch
videos.description: November 17 has been circled on the schedule. The Broncos head back to Scott County.
